				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%E1%BA%A3i-T%C3%ADnh-Phu/Bi%E1%BB%87t-ly-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-bJ5CoGaPksALamluB-x17Q">Biệt ly từ kỳ 1 - 別離詞其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%E1%BA%A3i-T%C3%ADnh-Phu/author-5VBdkDLCcLTpFT7k3ZzmYg">Ngải Tính Phu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Giang-Y%C3%AAm/Chinh-o%C3%A1n/poem-QUMfE9cgJPhd21pFnymwXw">Chinh oán - 征怨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Giang-Y%C3%AAm/author-BvX7SZcYDh6BIaZimIwj-Q">Giang Yêm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/%C4%90%E1%BA%AFc-gia-th%C6%B0-th%E1%BB%8B-nh%E1%BA%ADt-t%C3%A1c/poem-w52NGg4k0na_rajDMu1bmg">Đắc gia thư, thị nhật tác - 得家書是日作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%8Bnh-L%E1%BB%B1c-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/K%E1%BB%87/poem-c9h45Qum1WlcNIHwjrmJVg">Kệ - 偈</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%8Bnh-L%E1%BB%B1c-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-zGrS2c5NIzw4-9JtGZbUkA">Tịnh Lực thiền sư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Gi%E1%BA%A3-V%C3%A2n-Hoa/K%C3%BD-Ngu%E1%BB%B5-B%E1%BA%B1ng-k%E1%BB%B3-04/poem-l6cJpV0ucc2ETyxLMtKhUw">Ký Nguỵ Bằng kỳ 04 - 寄魏鵬其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Gi%E1%BA%A3-V%C3%A2n-Hoa/author-Se3JVs_zS4GXJWFmZ5v2og">Giả Vân Hoa</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B3-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/Th%E1%BA%BF-s%E1%BB%B1-thi/poem-oLuBZ4cVdK1Mb_Al9mFcwg">Thế sự thi - 世事詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B3-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/author-03ZNaWfxP9_K2e7vJXYXyw">Kỳ Đồng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/Th%C3%B9-Qu%C3%A1ch-c%E1%BA%A5p-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-6wYeG3m6ykAeKUPgpfTdZw">Thù Quách cấp sự - 酬郭給事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%A9a-H%E1%BB%93n/T%E1%BB%91ng-Ti%E1%BA%BFt-t%C3%BA-t%C3%A0i-nam-du/poem-j1ZeReIyR4KwWAlP5PBjiw">Tống Tiết tú tài nam du - 送薛秀才南遊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%A9a-H%E1%BB%93n/author-67u8r1Npo8IzUDBZnVHSFA">Hứa Hồn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Th%E1%BB%A5c-Ch%C3%A2n/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-ho%C3%A0i-l%E1%BB%87/poem-SNSbg97GRcY2FQqS5-CAQg">Xuân nhật hoài lệ - 春日懷淚</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Th%E1%BB%A5c-Ch%C3%A2n/author-i-czuf5WvTrcNJ1FAmZhMw">Chu Thục Chân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/Y%E1%BA%BFt-S%C6%A1n/poem-oH7Plkf-z--WaPfyFGZvaQ">Yết Sơn - 謁山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
